# Inecta ETL

INGESTION

inectaETL provides a comprehensive set of pre-configured data transformations from Microsoft Business Central, quickly pipelined into MotherDuck within minutes, so you can:

- Easily extend the pipeline by adding more datasets as needed

- Seamlessly integrate new data sources without interrupting operations

- Ensure complete, accurate, and up-to-date data is always visible
